 mini-landscape picture from the\nmass pattern expected in models with gaugino mass unification. The thermal WIMP\nsignal should be accessible via direct detection searches at the multi-ton\nnoble liquid detectors such as Xenon-nT or LZ.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2017 18:52:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-02"}
