trained Au$_2$Y$_3$ and\nHg$_2$Sr$_3$ host related topological surface hourglass fermions. We also\nreport the presence of this new topological hourglass phase in\nBa$_5$In$_2$Sb$_6$ in SG 55. For orthorhombic space groups with two glides, we\ncatalog all possible bulk topological phases by a consideration of the allowed\nnon-abelian Wilson loop connectivities, and we develop topological invariants\nfor these systems. Finally, we show how in a particular limit, these\ncrystalline phases reduce to copies of the SSH model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 May 2017 20:46:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 21 Jul 2018 11:59:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-24"}
