s. However, this is unlikely, as our model suggests strong deceleration to\nspeeds < 0.5c within months and a much smaller, sub-parsec size. In this\ninterpretation, the northwest component could have either a non-nuclear origin\nor be from an earlier event.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 May 2017 01:38:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 May 2017 18:29:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
